The paper deals with the analysis of paging algorithms, which is a topic in data structures (cs.DS) and algorithms (cs.AL). The use of access graphs also involves information theory (cs.IT) and probabilistic analysis (cs.PF). Finally, the comparison of different algorithms can be seen as a form of computational complexity theory (cs.CC).
